	12. Watanabe, F., Katsura, H., Takenaka, S., Fujita, T., Abe, K., Tamura, Y., Nakatsuka, T., Nakano, Y. Pseudovitamin B(12) is the predominant cobamide of an algal health food, spirulina tablets. _Journal of Agricultural and Food Chemistry_ 1999, 47(11):4736-41. Виж също: Vegetarian Society UK fact sheet. „Vitamin B{sub}12{/sub}“ http://www.vegsoc.org/info/B12.html
